OL,4,CTrust in news has grown in the UK
OL,5,Cduring pandemic, research shows
OL,6, Trust in news coverage has grown in the
OL,7, UK with the public appetite for
OL,8, reliable reporting increasing during
OL,9, the pandemic, research suggests.
OL,11,FThe Reuters Institute Digital News
OL,12,FReport, conducted in January this year,
OL,13,Ffound that 36% of people in the UK
OL,14,F"trust most news most of the time".
OL,16,FThat figure is up from 28% in January
OL,17,F2020, before the pandemic began.
OL,19,FBut it is still 14 percentage points
OL,20,Fdown on where it was prior to the
OL,21,FBrexit vote in 2016.
